<section id="pillars">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="skick">The four pillars</p>
    <h2 class="sh">Real frameworks, not <em>vibes</em>.</h2>
    <p class="sintro">
      Zuly starts with a conversation, then guides you through the pillars that fit your season — each
      grounded in what actually works.
    </p>
    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pil" style="--pc:var(--gold)">
        <span class="pn">01</span>
        <h3>Meditation</h3>
        <p>Grounding, breath, and calm you can keep — short daily practice that fits a real life.</p>
        <span class="ev">Built on MBSR / MBCT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pil" style="--pc:var(--spark)">
        <span class="pn">02</span>
        <h3>Self-healing</h3>
        <p>Journaling, reframing, and self-compassion to move through what's heavy — with Zuly to talk to.</p>
        <span class="ev">CBT &amp; expressive writing</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pil" style="--pc:var(--oxblood)">
        <span class="pn">03</span>
        <h3>Body</h3>
        <p>Movement that builds over weeks, not punishes — paced to your body and your goals.</p>
        <span class="ev">Progressive, periodized</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pil" style="--pc:var(--gold)">
        <span class="pn">04</span>
        <h3>Life guidance</h3>
        <p>Relationships, work, money, self — small guided principles that compound into change.</p>
        <span class="ev">Habit &amp; behavior design</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
